		<h2 class="heading">Trending <svg role="img" class="icon icon--trending" aria-label="trending"><use xlink:href="https://calmatters.org/wp-content/themes/thenewsproject/dist/svg/dist/symbol/svg/sprite.symbol.svg#trending"></use></svg></h2>

		<ul id="menu-top-trending-1" class="topics"><li class="menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-105092"><a href="https://calmatters.org/category/health/coronavirus/">Coronavirus Coverage</a></li>
